text: Bonsall is a census designated place (CDP) in San Diego County, California, United States. It is east of Oceanside and Marine Corps Base Camp Pendleton. In 2020, Bonsall had 4,546 people. == Climate == == Other websites == * Bonsall Unified School District == References == Category:Census-designated places in California Category:Settlements in San Diego County, California
